'''''18 Hours''''' ni film yikinamico yo muri Kenya 2017 yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Njue Kevin kumugaragaro bwa mbere<ref>18 Hours (2017) - Showmax Stories <nowiki>https://stories.showmax.com</nowiki> › 18-hours-movie</ref>.  Abakinnyi barimo Nick Ndeda, Sue Wanjiru, Brian Ogola, Isaya Evans na Shirleen Wangari<ref>18 Hours, movie on city ambulance patient, premieres <nowiki>https://nairobinews.nation.co.ke</nowiki> › 18-hours-movie-amb...</ref>. Iyi filime "ikurikira inkeragutabara ya rookie irokoka amasaha 18 muri ambulance ubuzima bw'impanuka yo mu muhanda yangiwe kwinjira mu bitaro<ref>The true story behind Kenyan medical thriller 18 Hours <nowiki>https://www.screenafrica.com</nowiki> › film › film-content › th...</ref>."  Iyi filime, yakoze amateka nk’ifoto ya mbere yo muri Kenya yatowe muri Filime Nziza Muri rusange muri Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards ( AMVCA ) yegukana ibindi 4 bahatanira ibihembo muri 2018<ref>The 5 Best Kenyan Movies Of 2017 - Dream Africa <nowiki>https://www.thedreamafrica.com</nowiki> › ... › Film & TV</ref>. 

