== Umusaruro ==
Igitekerezo cya firime cyatangiye mu 2015 ubwo Njue Kevin, umwanditsi & diregiteri, yasomaga inkuru ku kinyamakuru<ref>Kenyan movie '18 hours' bags 5 nominations - The Standard <nowiki>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke</nowiki> › local-news › kenyan...</ref>.  Ninkuru yahumetswe namakuba yabayeho, aho umugabo yavuye ambulance mumasaha 18 kuko ibitaro byigihugu bya Kenyatta(Kenyatta National Hospital) byavugaga ko bidafite uburiri bwa ICU(ICU bed)<ref>18 Hours - Paukwa <nowiki>https://paukwa.or.ke</nowiki> › 18-hours</ref>.  Nibwo twatangiye gukina hirya no hino twibwira ko iyi idashobora kuba film ikomeye; twibwira ko ari firime yo kwishimisha ariko ikanakoreshwa muguhindura imibereho. <ref>5 facts about 18 Hours - the true Kenyan story turned into film <nowiki>https://www.pulselive.co.ke</nowiki> › Entertainment › Movies</ref> Producer, Phoebe Ruguru yahise yomekwa hanyuma iterambere ryimyandikire ritangirana no kuvugana nabaganga benshi nabatekinisiye byihutirwa bari barinjiye rwose kandi bafite uruhare mumushinga hose. <ref>CENTRESTAGE: Emotional ‘18 hours’ hits cinemas | Kenya (nation.africa)</ref> Njue yabitangaje, kubwibyo twagombaga kuba abizerwa mubuvandimwe, nkuko Njue yabitangarije BBC Gahuzamiryango. <ref>BBC Minute: On bringing life to the screen <nowiki>https://www.bbc.co.uk</nowiki> › Programmes › BBC Minute</ref>

Igikorwa cyo gukina cyari cy'itabiriwe nabantu kandi cy'itabiriwe n'abakinnyi ba Kenya nubwo umusaruro wakiriye ibyifuzo by'abakinnyi kwisi yose harimo bamwe bo muri LA, Hollywood, London, nu Budage<ref>Rafiki director Wanuri Kahiu on Cannes success and Kenya ban <nowiki>https://www.bbc.com</nowiki> › news › world-africa-44163251</ref>.  Ihamagarwa rya casting ryashyizwe k'umurongo kandi ryakiriye abasaba 1000 hanyuma 25 gusa binjira muri firime. <ref>Africa highlights: Monday 3 July 2017 as it happened - BBC News <nowiki>https://www.bbc.com</nowiki> › live › world-africa-39660295 › L...</ref> Nyuma yo kwandika, Njue yahaye akazi umuhanzi w'inkuru maze akambika ibyumweru 4 mu nzu ye i Nairobi  aho bakoze ibishushanyo n'amashusho kugira ngo basobanure inkuru<ref>18 Hours (2017) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>.

